 10 亿美元的协议，以取消联邦水域的租赁。彭博新闻联系道达尔代表时拒绝置评，内政部也没有回应置评请求。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;&lt;em style="font-size: 16px;"&gt;阅读&lt;/em&gt;&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/AwFq2YsEVxvTHVqK4yiR6-WZvYTAyZF9Q0QRnAgRL0OtxrrYnj334ZhDh4nosOQTy0Rm1wEYvf8ftAroF-t2nHtWLYU1WB7ypcq1jdPThabaImJgMB4rye5G84bFpAR_HncW6SQk9qBk6DdryGr4HVwr9tqUMA6dkY3H5jxmiKLVNaM0gAvlHFSu3c0MepC9A4pBLrPS9X-rQ_xynv-nzt7AlVScfttvrX2TDbwniQgUgUSAvUwYW9IYmj9OtKUuzflNwJ1PrOdIP5scu65gHD1WfXvwZVX48Swl6GdaXmIw_JnwRGF-S_UsbvqsvNPskwRiCAGn5dueMV5ITpj8hQNppU_lQtVNCG8jUxIQhfJ4I6eOtNCnoiY8faSv6OGw1WBRB3FK505v710uUMp7iO5yX1iWw42G0IbZldANI9IunZLKQRJPFJYw6USCkiZL0O9bIFnFs6u_rwtLKM-QymNOUCpCkfG91CGHvIvLwsh5mpEEHqJ5mVAJSlIAeZvig7HjvTJ8Fzg8p5YESgf6bd-3vSo-tLs/5uWpeVjdm62oJtmXUIxcKvXGaUYl39II/18" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="特朗普再次发誓在总统任期内阻止风力涡轮机"&gt;&lt;em style="font-size: 16px;"&gt;全文&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;em style="font-size: 16px;"&gt;。&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-size: 16px;"&gt;参议员马克韦恩·穆林不支持&lt;/strong&gt;废除联邦紧急事务管理局，而是&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/w6Cla0EuFUDtXKcVEaBJI1pVyX3z9aYvZYK8yqLhgeFbvfjsDQHebR0cIn0mvrMUHeTiCE5R2bbMViU5TJ-sUyF8FZv4bhwnoVQmCTbk7iVpAxcOHCP6Il053GzqEiIfRIV4eB2PusrKEvWjQoQ9EOOTqitwB3AS_ZzhJxEtFF8Eb98vq4MGjTvDhqDu8_yvAGqILcIE5Chuh94oPg995vCadx2oXj9gAWHoU_zaqu3EpFLXKm6X_-66VTMXOlHb_MpEDCM7v_4m87UkAN_Je9npuXrERh0NWM481RyN5csB6xfb5xLJGSf78U6djY9-k2YrrtORLA7JxmvzmBQ9BIVPYHY_e9iXU0__dfUxGs7ur6Swno1yJLAXjvGnGvXlUGmHI7FvqlY/bZpu-Ar9iqoj240s9gvCzYK2QZQym-2h/18" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="穆林承诺结束联邦应急管理局资金的“微观管理”政策"&gt;赞成进行重组&lt;/a&gt;。这位共和党人已被提名领导国土安全部，负责监督联邦应急管理局。他还表示，他将结束对该机构财务的“微观管理”。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-size: 16px;"&gt;美国已经有足够的能力&lt;/strong&gt;来建设&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloo